6.11	Versant	Versant	The Versant suite of tests are computerized tests of spoken language available from Pearson. Versant tests were the first fully automated tests of spoken language to use advanced speech processing technology (including speech recognition) to assess the spoken language skills of non-native speakers. The Versant language suite includes tests of English, Spanish, and Arabic. Versant technology has also been applied to the assessment of Aviation English, childrenâ€™s oral reading assessment, and adult literacy assessment.	
